## What Not To Do

- Do not modify `prisma/migrations/`. If a schema change requires a new migration, generate it with `prisma migrate dev`.
- Do not edit `src/lib/auth.ts` without explaining the change and flagging it.
- Do not add new npm packages without listing them in your response.
- Do not commit secrets, API keys, or `.env` files.
- Do not write to the database in test files without cleaning up after.
- Do not use `console.log` in production code. Use the logger at `src/lib/logger.ts`.
